    "result": {"data":{"markdownRemark":{"excerpt":"Hi Friends 👋, Welcome To aGuideHub!  To make mui toggle button with tooltip in react js, you have to use  component in ToggleButtonGroup component. it will…","html":"<p>Hi Friends 👋,</p>\n<p>Welcome To aGuideHub! </p>\n<p>To make mui toggle button with tooltip in react js, you have to use <code class=\"language-text\">&lt;Tooltip title=\"Add\"></code> component in ToggleButtonGroup component. it will make mui toggle button with tooltip in React JS.</p>\n<p>Today, I am going to show you, How to make mui toggle button with tooltip in react js</p>\n<h2>Installation</h2>\n<p>Install the following packages to use mui toggle button in react js.</p>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">npm</code></p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"js\"><pre class=\"language-js\"><code class=\"language-js\">npm install @mui<span class=\"token operator\">/</span>material @emotion<span class=\"token operator\">/</span>react @emotion<span class=\"token operator\">/</span>styled</code></pre></div>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">yarn</code></p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"js\"><pre class=\"language-js\"><code class=\"language-js\">yarn add @mui<span class=\"token operator\">/</span>material @emotion<span class=\"token operator\">/</span>react @emotion<span class=\"token operator\">/</span>styled</code></pre></div>\n<p>Table of contents</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Install MUI and create a new React app.</li>\n<li>Import Material-UI toggle button.</li>\n<li>Use the toggle button Component.</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>Step 1: Install MUI and create a new React app.</h3>\n<p>First you have to install the React project. You should use <code class=\"language-text\">create-react-app</code> command to create a new React project.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"js\"><pre class=\"language-js\"><code class=\"language-js\">npx create<span class=\"token operator\">-</span>react<span class=\"token operator\">-</span>app my<span class=\"token operator\">-</span>app\ncd my<span class=\"token operator\">-</span>app\nnpm start</code></pre></div>\n<h3>Step 2: Import Material-UI toggle button.</h3>\n<p>After installing <code class=\"language-text\">MUI</code>, you have to import your React component. To do this, add the following line to the top of your component file.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"js\"><pre class=\"language-js\"><code class=\"language-js\"><span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> <span class=\"token operator\">*</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">as</span> React <span class=\"token keyword\">from</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"react\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> FormatAlignLeftIcon <span class=\"token keyword\">from</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"@mui/icons-material/FormatAlignLeft\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> FormatAlignCenterIcon <span class=\"token keyword\">from</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"@mui/icons-material/FormatAlignCenter\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> FormatAlignRightIcon <span class=\"token keyword\">from</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"@mui/icons-material/FormatAlignRight\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> FormatAlignJustifyIcon <span class=\"token keyword\">from</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"@mui/icons-material/FormatAlignJustify\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> ToggleButton <span class=\"token keyword\">from</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"@mui/material/ToggleButton\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> ToggleButtonGroup <span class=\"token keyword\">from</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"@mui/material/ToggleButtonGroup\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> Tooltip <span class=\"token keyword\">from</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"@mui/material/Tooltip\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>\n<h3>Step 3: Use the toggle button Component.</h3>\n<p>Toggle Button Group provides a way to get mutually exclusive actions closer together by sharing a common container.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"js\"><pre class=\"language-js\"><code class=\"language-js\"><span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>Tooltip title<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token string\">\"Add\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n    <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>ToggleButtonGroup\n        value<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>alignment<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n        exclusive\n        onChange<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>handleAlignment<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n        aria<span class=\"token operator\">-</span>label<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token string\">\"text alignment\"</span>\n      <span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n      <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>ToggleButton value<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token string\">\"left\"</span> aria<span class=\"token operator\">-</span>label<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token string\">\"left aligned\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n          <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>FormatAlignLeftIcon <span class=\"token operator\">/</span><span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n      <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token operator\">/</span>ToggleButton<span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n      <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>ToggleButton value<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token string\">\"center\"</span> aria<span class=\"token operator\">-</span>label<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token string\">\"centered\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n          <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>FormatAlignCenterIcon <span class=\"token operator\">/</span><span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n      <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token operator\">/</span>ToggleButton<span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n      <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>ToggleButton value<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token string\">\"right\"</span> aria<span class=\"token operator\">-</span>label<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token string\">\"right aligned\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n          <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>FormatAlignRightIcon <span class=\"token operator\">/</span><span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n      <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token operator\">/</span>ToggleButton<span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n      <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>ToggleButton value<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token string\">\"justify\"</span> aria<span class=\"token operator\">-</span>label<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token string\">\"justified\"</span> disabled<span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n          <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>FormatAlignJustifyIcon <span class=\"token operator\">/</span><span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n      <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token operator\">/</span>ToggleButton<span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n    <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token operator\">/</span>ToggleButtonGroup<span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n<span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token operator\">/</span>Tooltip<span class=\"token operator\">></span></code></pre></div>\n<h2>MUI material make mui toggle button with tooltip example.</h2>\n<p>The below code is an example, you need to import <code class=\"language-text\">toggle button</code> Component. Then, you have to use <code class=\"language-text\">&lt;Tooltip title=\"Add\"></code> component in ToggleButtonGroup component. Then it will make mui toggle button with tooltip in react js.</p>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">App.js</code></p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"js\"><pre class=\"language-js\"><code class=\"language-js\"><span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> <span class=\"token operator\">*</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">as</span> React <span class=\"token keyword\">from</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"react\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> FormatAlignLeftIcon <span class=\"token keyword\">from</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"@mui/icons-material/FormatAlignLeft\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> FormatAlignCenterIcon <span class=\"token keyword\">from</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"@mui/icons-material/FormatAlignCenter\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> FormatAlignRightIcon <span class=\"token keyword\">from</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"@mui/icons-material/FormatAlignRight\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> FormatAlignJustifyIcon <span class=\"token keyword\">from</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"@mui/icons-material/FormatAlignJustify\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> ToggleButton <span class=\"token keyword\">from</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"@mui/material/ToggleButton\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> ToggleButtonGroup <span class=\"token keyword\">from</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"@mui/material/ToggleButtonGroup\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> Tooltip <span class=\"token keyword\">from</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"@mui/material/Tooltip\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">export</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">default</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"token function\">ToggleButtons</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>alignment<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> setAlignment<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> React<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">useState</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"left\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> <span class=\"token function-variable function\">handleAlignment</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token parameter\">event<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> newAlignment</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=></span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token function\">setAlignment</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>newAlignment<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>\n    <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>Tooltip title<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token string\">\"Add\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n      <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>ToggleButtonGroup\n        value<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>alignment<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n        exclusive\n        onChange<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>handleAlignment<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n        aria<span class=\"token operator\">-</span>label<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token string\">\"text alignment\"</span>\n      <span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n        <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>ToggleButton value<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token string\">\"left\"</span> aria<span class=\"token operator\">-</span>label<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token string\">\"left aligned\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n          <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>FormatAlignLeftIcon <span class=\"token operator\">/</span><span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n        <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token operator\">/</span>ToggleButton<span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n        <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>ToggleButton value<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token string\">\"center\"</span> aria<span class=\"token operator\">-</span>label<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token string\">\"centered\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n          <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>FormatAlignCenterIcon <span class=\"token operator\">/</span><span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n        <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token operator\">/</span>ToggleButton<span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n        <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>ToggleButton value<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token string\">\"right\"</span> aria<span class=\"token operator\">-</span>label<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token string\">\"right aligned\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n          <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>FormatAlignRightIcon <span class=\"token operator\">/</span><span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n        <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token operator\">/</span>ToggleButton<span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n        <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>ToggleButton value<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token string\">\"justify\"</span> aria<span class=\"token operator\">-</span>label<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token string\">\"justified\"</span> disabled<span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n          <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>FormatAlignJustifyIcon <span class=\"token operator\">/</span><span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n        <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token operator\">/</span>ToggleButton<span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n      <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token operator\">/</span>ToggleButtonGroup<span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n    <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token operator\">/</span>Tooltip<span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>In the above code example, I have used the <code class=\"language-text\">@mui/material</code> component and make mui toggle button with tooltip in react js.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-w